scene.message:
Nanjo: Kandori and I never{nl}
hit it off, from the first{nl}
time we met at a party.{waitkey}If only I'd seen through his{nl}
scheme back then...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: There's a chance we{nl}
could end up dead, after all.{wait_fr:32}{nl}
I don't really mind, but{waitkey}{clearbox}my old lady... {wait_fr:32}when I think{nl}
of Mom crying, it just bugs{nl}
me...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Let's hurry up and go{nl}
crush this Kandori guy!{waitkey}Idiot, like I'd ever be{wait_fr:16}{nl}
s-{wait_fr:16}scared, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Go after Kandori,{nl}
quick...{wait_fr:32} we really do have{nl}
to chase him, huh...?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase's not scared or{nl}
anything{wait_fr:48}... okay, maybe just{nl}
a little scared.{waitkey}{ret}
